</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Thereâ€™s a lot of information in there, but we are really only concerned with the payload of the response, the meat, the information we are looking for, which is stored in the body.</p>

<p>So we look at what <code class="highlighter-rouge">response.body</code> will return.</p>

