<h2 id="extension">Extension</h2>

<p>In addition to printing the name for each person, print out the name of each film they appear in.</p>

<p>There are multiple ways to go about this. Here are some tips:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Donâ€™t be afraid to make multiple API calls</li>
  <li>Try to make the API do as much work for you as possible</li>
</ul>
